PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FExperts have said Noah may have died
OL,8,Fon the same day he went missing,
OL,9,FSunday June 21 2020, or could
OL,10,Fpotentially have survived until
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,13,FHis naked body was found in a storm
OL,14,Fdrain tunnel in north Belfast by
OL,15,Fpolice on Saturday June 27, six days
OL,16,Fafter he left home on his bike
OL,17,Fbelieved to have been intending to
OL,18,Fmeet two friends in the Cavehill area
OL,19,Fof the city.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Justice Rooney emphasised to the
OL,8,Fjury that only errors which they find
OL,9,Fhappened before Noah died can be
OL,10,Fattributed as potentially having
OL,11,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,13,FHe started his lengthy summing up to
OL,14,Fthe jury of eight men and two women on
OL,15,FThursday, during the 21st week of the
OL,16,Finquest, which started in January.
OL,18,FHe continued his charge to the jury on
OL,19,FMonday morning, and completed it by
OL,20,Fjust before 6pm that evening, adding
OL,21,Fhis thanks to jurors for staying on.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
