PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe jury is to be sent out on Tuesday
OL,8,Fto formally start their considerations.
OL,10,FThey have been tasked with reaching
OL,11,Funanimous findings by agreeing answers
OL,12,Fto a questionnaire prepared for them
OL,13,Fwith input from the properly
OL,14,Finterested parties in the proceedings.
OL,16,FIt comes after almost six months of
OL,17,Fevidence at Belfast Coroner's Court
OL,18,Fincluding 76 witnesses, statements
OL,19,Ffrom a further 42 people, as well as
OL,20,Fmaps, video footage, photographs,
OL,21,Fpolice logs and expert reports.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
