PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,9,Fin the storm drain tunnel in north
OL,10,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,11,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,12,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of the
OL,13,Fcity.
OL,15,FCCTV evidence and witnesses show that
OL,16,FNoah took a detour from his planned
OL,17,Froute, cycling instead along York Road
OL,18,Fand ended up on Northwood Road where
OL,19,Fit is suggested he entered the tunnel
OL,20,Fvia a culvert behind a house.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe inquest was shown CCTV of Noah
OL,8,Fcycling naked along Northwood Road,
OL,9,Fand evidence that some residents heard
OL,10,Fnoises including screams on the night
OL,11,Fof June 21 when Noah went missing.
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,14,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,16,FThe jury is charged with reaching
OL,17,Ffindings including how Noah came by
OL,18,Fhis death.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe, who has
OL,8,Fled a high-profile campaign for
OL,9,Fanswers around her son's death, has
OL,10,Fbeen present at Belfast Coroner's
OL,11,FCourt for every day of the inquest.
OL,13,FOn Monday, Mr Rooney told the jury it
OL,14,Fis for them to assess what police
OL,15,Fknew, when they knew it, and what they
OL,16,Fdid in response.
OL,18,F"Your role is to consider police
OL,19,Factions, and whether they contributed,
OL,20,Fmore than minimally, to his (Noah's)
OL,21,Fdeath," he said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe coroner made clear that errors can
OL,8,Finclude something that was done, as as
OL,9,Fwell as something that was not done
OL,10,Fthat "more likely than not contributed
OL,11,Fto Noah's death".
OL,13,FBut he said only if those errors took
OL,14,Fplace before Noah died.
OL,26,@rD@FOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
