PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Justice Rooney reminded the jury of
OL,8,Fthe evidence they had heard in the
OL,9,Fcase from when Ms Donohoe has first
OL,10,Freported Noah missing at 9.44pm on
OL,11,FSunday June 21 and the start of the
OL,12,Fsearch, to tracking down CCTV footage
OL,13,Fof Noah's journey, witness reports,
OL,14,Fretrieval of Noah's phone and laptop
OL,15,Fand physical search efforts from door-
OL,16,Fto-door inquiries and searching in the
OL,17,Ftunnel.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe told jurors that questions have
OL,8,Fbeen prepared with input from the
OL,9,Fproperly interested parties for them
OL,10,Fto answer with their findings around
OL,11,Fthe circumstances in which Noah came
OL,12,Fby his death, which he said will form
OL,13,Fpart of the record of the inquest.
OL,15,FThe questions range from yes or no
OL,16,Fanswers to those that demand narrative
OL,17,Fresponses, and from a factual account
OL,18,Fof Noah's death to questions around
OL,19,Fthe actions of police and around the
OL,20,Fculvert where it is believed he
OL,21,Fentered the storm drain.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
