OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782850701
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe inquest jury to decide
OL,4,Cwhether police error contributed to
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe emphasised their findings should be
OL,8,Fmade on the evidence they saw and
OL,9,Fheard during the inquest, adding they
OL,10,Fshould take as long as they need to in
OL,11,Forder to reach their conclusions.
OL,13,FThe jury is expected to be formally
OL,14,Fsent out to start their deliberations
OL,15,Fon Tuesday morning.
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
